channel.title: Need help installing the newest JDK update
channel.description:
hello everyone, i need help badly... im trying to get the newest update in java.. idk what happened to my other java files.. and i cannot code anything AT ALL with the version i now have.. which is like the 2003 jdk version.. on plateform 2... when i try to download/install any java update i get a message in a dialog box saying this... "error 1606: could not access network %APPDATA%\."
Anyone can help? i would like if so.. thanks.. hope i get the help i need..

change the environmental variables to whatever version of java you have, Ex. I have 13 so i would put C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin;%CLASSPATH%;
